\c 2
\s Ukuhlamuka kukaIsrayeli
\p
\v 1 Laselifika kimi ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lisithi:
\v 2 Hamba u\add ye\add*memezela endlebeni zeJerusalema usithi: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Ngiyakukhumbula, umusa wobutsha bakho,\x + 3.4. Hlab. 129.1.\x* uthando lokuganwa kwakho,\x + 3.14. Hez. 16.8,22,43,60. Isam. 2.4.\x* ukungilandela kwakho enkangala,\x + Dute. 2.7.\x* elizweni \add e\add*lingahlanyelwanga.\x + Dute. 8.2,3. Amos 2.10.\x*
\v 3 UIsrayeli wayeyibungcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni,\x + Eks. 19.5,6; 28.26.\x* izithelo zokuqala zesivuno sayo;\x + Jak. 1.18.\x* bonke abamudlayo bazakuba lecala,\x + 50.7. Hez. 25.12.\x* ububi buzabehlela,\x + 12.14.\x* itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 4 Zwanini ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*, ndlu kaJakobe, lensendo zonke zendlu kaIsrayeli.
