\v 24 Ungubabhemi weganga\x + 14.6.\x*\x + Jobe 6.5. Gen. 16.12. Jobe 11.12. Hos. 8.9.\x* \add o\add*wejwayele inkangala, \add o\add*phembela umoya enkanukweni yenhliziyo yakhe.\x + 14.6.\x* Ngubani ongamvimbela \add e\add*nkanuk\add weni\add* yakhe?\x + Hlu. 14.4.\x* Bonke abamdingayo kabayikuzidinisa; ngenyanga yakhe bazamthola.\x + 1 Kho. 4.27.\x*
